name: What A Lovely Name The Name Of Jesus
chorusText:
What a lovely Name, the Name of Jesus
reaching higher far, than the brightest star
sweeter than the songs, they sing in heaven
let the world proclaim, what a lovely Name

He made the stars to shine, He made the rolling sea
He made the mountains high, and He made me
and this is why I love Him, for He has bled and died
The Lord of all creations, became the Crucified
